{"id": "1349230748137164862", "channel_id": "1349229925940596776", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "7.隧道奇遇記-Tunnel Adventure-\n地下鐵中遭到攻擊雖然不幸，但作為滿足女孩好奇心的餘興節目，卻是剛剛好。\nAlthough it was unfortunate to be attacked in the subway, it was just right as an entertainment program to satisfy the girl's curiosity.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T04:01:17.851000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349230747633979483", "filename": "7.-Tunnel_Adventure-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 34798972, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349229925940596776/1349230747633979483/7.-Tunnel_Adventure-.wav?ex=69cc988d&is=69cb470d&hm=f538bf15cbe6839d46a625f078b7e1a834c7f78cb427fae44fea7ffb4dd3da4d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349229925940596776", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：雪落噬影之鎮", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
