{"id": "1349230943839322113", "channel_id": "1349229925940596776", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "10.痛苦回憶-Painful Memories-\n潮水湧起，尖嘯迴盪，痛苦的回憶湧上心頭，將女孩的精神撕碎。眼角流下的黑色淚水，是她發出的無聲呼救。\nThe tide surged, the screams echoed, and the painful memories surged into the heart, tearing the girl's spirit apart. The black tears flowing from the corners of her eyes were her silent cry for help.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T04:02:04.510000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349230943637864519", "filename": "10.-Painful_Memories-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 32907232, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349229925940596776/1349230943637864519/10.-Painful_Memories-.wav?ex=69cc98bc&is=69cb473c&hm=ea29726109852f1cc86057df119ca52d137b24047f0fe5311b76eb0c81fb9cec&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349229925940596776", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：雪落噬影之鎮", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349231074328313867", "channel_id": "1349229925940596776", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "11.被拋棄者-The Abandoned-\n拋棄與背叛是高位者的家常便飯，不要將後背露給他們，防止變成最後的光與熱。\nAbandonment and betrayal are commonplace for those in high positions. Don't show your back to them, to prevent it from becoming the last light and warmth.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T04:02:35.621000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349231074080854016", "filename": "11.-The_Abandoned-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 34531444, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349229925940596776/1349231074080854016/11.-The_Abandoned-.wav?ex=69cc98db&is=69cb475b&hm=8f157af614e9ee48433b4b05cc55e6b25f3f23bd736133d7f9bbc52d7a8924a4&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349229925940596776", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：雪落噬影之鎮", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349231180364648448", "channel_id": "1349229925940596776", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "12.癲狂執念-Obsessive Madness-\n血肉翻飛，利刃狂舞，怪物用無法理解的言語高聲歌唱。狂暴的大腦中只剩下一個念頭──抓住她，不惜一切代價，抓住她。\nBlood and flesh flew, blades danced wildly, and monsters sang loudly in incomprehensible words. There was only one thought left in the violent brain - catch her, catch her at all costs.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T04:03:00.902000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1349231180012191795", "filename": "12.-Obsessive_Madness-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 45767716, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349229925940596776/1349231180012191795/12.-Obsessive_Madness-.wav?ex=69cc98f4&is=69cb4774&hm=f818f7a26bf0b509a0b1db40d1ddaa2d5738dd575bd3723b76745cdc3d1a1fbd&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349229925940596776", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：雪落噬影之鎮", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
