{"id": "1349219168112869460", "channel_id": "1349218982866980864", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "1. 悲鳴黑膠-Grooved Lament-\n黑膠唱片撕扯著黏稠的喉嚨，引亢不甘的悲鳴。\nThe vinyl record tore at the sticky throat, causing an unwilling wail.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T03:15:16.958000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349219168066470200", "filename": "1.-Grooved_Lament-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 25705190, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349218982866980864/1349219168066470200/1.-Grooved_Lament-.wav?ex=69cc8dc4&is=69cb3c44&hm=b19bba5f0ba0757accf2bff9ba73b199c96d70b21dd52acbfa6212a7c36f45a2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349218982866980864", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：復甦黑日之世", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349219445729656932", "channel_id": "1349218982866980864", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "2.腦髓製造-Brain Manufacturing-\n這裡生產的並非普通工業品。\nWhat is produced here are not ordinary industrial products.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T03:16:23.147000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349219445309964350", "filename": "2.-Brain_Manufacturing-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 33581506, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349218982866980864/1349219445309964350/2.-Brain_Manufacturing-.wav?ex=69cc8e07&is=69cb3c87&hm=77dff388790dd9086a2ba09cfb5a17a359b4b5d8d95b4f4fba0aa9545a0ba80a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349218982866980864", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：復甦黑日之世", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349219961570070630", "channel_id": "1349218982866980864", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "3.崩毀變奏-Partita Collapse-\n崩毀的音符在舞蹈，坍塌的現實在喧囂。連夢的觸角都不涉足此地。\nThe collapsing notes are dancing, and the collapsing reality is roaring. Even the tentacles of dreams do not set foot here.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T03:18:26.133000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349219961226399824", "filename": "3.-Partita_Collapse-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 40382288, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349218982866980864/1349219961226399824/3.-Partita_Collapse-.wav?ex=69cc8e82&is=69cb3d02&hm=40dccf138f6a1fe8abe6d6c23f420f97ef5726492e7c2ed398e2a8cb80a12cc2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349218982866980864", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：復甦黑日之世", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349220138368634932", "channel_id": "1349218982866980864", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "4.窒息煙塵-Soot Psalm-\n灰霧籠罩著黑色的太陽，粉塵填滿口鼻。勿要張口呼吸－希望已在先前埋葬。\nGray fog shrouded the black sun, and dust filled my mouth and nose. Don't breathe through your mouth - hope has been buried long ago.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T03:19:08.285000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349220137928097802", "filename": "4.-Soot_Psalm-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 22235914, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349218982866980864/1349220137928097802/4.-Soot_Psalm-.wav?ex=69cc8eac&is=69cb3d2c&hm=628327fb7e9b98a5fbb73551950712878b2f5f49987461a29ee9b5760b5fde8c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349218982866980864", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：復甦黑日之世", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349220293121675275", "channel_id": "1349218982866980864", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "5.黑日圖騰-Eclipse Glyph-\n遠空的黑色末日猶如天穹的孔洞。那是來自未揭露之地的圖騰。\nThe black apocalypse in the distance is like a hole in the sky. That is a totem from an unrevealed land.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T03:19:45.181000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349220292983128134", "filename": "5.-Eclipse_Glyph-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 23321848, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349218982866980864/1349220292983128134/5.-Eclipse_Glyph-.wav?ex=69cc8ed1&is=69cb3d51&hm=7d68826ad0cee06d5011f6e9b1c8a607c3ac2dac31e5dca612994f6073ce0c73&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349218982866980864", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：復甦黑日之世", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349220468133204002", "channel_id": "1349218982866980864", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "6.顱腔共振-Skull Resonance-\n打開你的顱腔，與千萬腦缸共振。答案或許就隱藏其中。\nOpen your cranial cavity and resonate with millions of brain tanks. The answer may be hidden there.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T03:20:26.907000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349220467927547986", "filename": "6.-Skull_Resonance-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 40940626, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349218982866980864/1349220467927547986/6.-Skull_Resonance-.wav?ex=69cc8efa&is=69cb3d7a&hm=3b649313d67167a0c531121b951323512391833b4214ac50311deca62167ad5b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349218982866980864", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：復甦黑日之世", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
