{"id": "1349272817551806474", "channel_id": "1349218982866980864", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "7.熔毀終末讚歌-Coda of Scorch-\n高唱吧，高唱吧！讓熔毀的機械奏鳴響徹寰宇，讚頌名為永恆黑暗的終末！\nSing loudly, sing loudly! Let the sonata of molten machinery resound throughout the universe, praising the end called eternal darkness!", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T06:48:27.981000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️‍🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1349272817153343538", "filename": "7.-Coda_of_Scorch-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 14038124, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349218982866980864/1349272817153343538/7.-Coda_of_Scorch-.mp3?ex=69ccbfbb&is=69cb6e3b&hm=6c6294c3c2f36dabd1102dadc84fc56be9e53aa4e6e0b9068507644789087b4b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349218982866980864", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：復甦黑日之世", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349273028915232768", "channel_id": "1349218982866980864", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "8.再見霏霏-Mistral Farewell-\n人生中的關鍵時刻，似乎總是有如絲細雨相伴。與那些霏霏細雨中的回憶告別吧，把釀成的苦酒深藏心底，握緊手中的銀鑰，踏上新的旅程。\n願銀鑰指引我們。\nThe critical moments in life always seem to be accompanied by drizzles. Say goodbye to those memories in the drizzle, hide the bitter wine deep in your heart, hold the silver key tightly in your hand, and embark on a new journey.\nMay the Silver Key guide us.", "timestamp": "2025-03-12T06:49:18.374000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349273028365647952", "filename": "8.-Mistral_Farewell-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 38874556, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349218982866980864/1349273028365647952/8.-Mistral_Farewell-.wav?ex=69ccbfee&is=69cb6e6e&hm=f059cf0927a9df4932c83380172acf8bec2272e1b66d5336aaa63bf2a52f15db&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349218982866980864", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：復甦黑日之世", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
